Solon Files Application for Opening of Insolvency Proceedings

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-12-13T19:19:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-13/solon-files-application-for-opening-of-insolvency-proceedings.html
Solon SE (SOO1)  said it has filed an
application for the opening of insolvency proceedings after the
company failed to reach “an amicable solution” with its banks
and investors regarding a financial restructuring.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Niklas Magnusson at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net  